{"thag2.32:0.1":"Theragatha 2.32 ","thag2.32:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.32:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag2.32:0.4":"Sivakattheragatha ","thag2.32:1.1":"“Aniccani gahakani, ","thag2.32:1.2":"tattha tattha punappunam; ","thag2.32:1.3":"Gahakaram gavesanto, ","thag2.32:1.4":"dukkha jati punappunam. ","thag2.32:2.1":"Gahakaraka ditthosi, ","thag2.32:2.2":"puna geham na kahasi; ","thag2.32:2.3":"Sabba te phasuka bhagga, ","thag2.32:2.4":"thunika ca vidalita; ","thag2.32:2.5":"Vimariyadikatam cittam, ","thag2.32:2.6":"idheva vidhamissati”ti. ","thag2.32:2.7":"… Sivako thero …. "}